--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
A        (Game) Assets
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
a_assets.js     - load game assets into memory and read them on-the-fly

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
AN       ANimation
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
an_animation.js - animate in-engine objects

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
G        Game loops and top-level stuff
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
g_const.js      - constants
g_main.js       - the main program
g_run.js        - game loops
g_setup.js      - setup routines

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
I        Interfaces, I/O controllers
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
i_input.js      - mouse & keyboard controller

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
M        Math
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
m_math.js       - math utilities
m_mat4.js       - 4x4 matrix
m_tri3.js       - 3-D triangle
m_vec3.js       - 3-D vector

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
R        Rendering
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
r_camera.js     - camera controller, and view & perspective transformations
r_draw.js       - rendering back-end--drawing routines
r_drawers.js    - render various menus, screens, etc.
r_geometry.js   - load, update & render 3-D geometry data
r_screen.js     - rendering front-end--access to framebuffer APIs

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
D        Data
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
mesh/d_*.js     - initial mesh data
d_player.js     - initial player data
d_textures.js   - texture lookup tables
